                    <img src="../../static/img/images/laser-clinics-candela-a-tailored-laser-hair-removal-for-you (1).png" id="height"
                        class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Laser hair removal</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Removal of unwanted hair using laser irradiation.</p>
                        <div class="modal fade" id="staticBackdrop" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false"
                            tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel" aria-hidden="true">
                            <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-scrollable">
                                <div class="modal-content">
                                    <div class="modal-header">
                                        <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="staticBackdropLabel">Massage</h1>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"
                                            aria-label="Close"></button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="modal-body">
                                        <p>
                                            How It Works:
                                            The laser targets the melanin in the hair follicle, which absorbs the light
                                            and converts it into heat.
                                            The heat damages the hair follicle, inhibiting its ability to produce new
                                            hair.
                                            <br>
                                            <hr>
                                            Suitability:
                                            Laser hair removal is most effective for individuals with dark hair and
                                            light skin because the laser can target the dark pigment more easily.
                                            Advances in technology have made it possible for individuals with darker
                                            skin tones to undergo laser hair removal, although results may vary.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button type="button" id="btn" class="btn btn-success" data-bs-toggle="modal"
                        data-bs-target="#staticBackdrop">Learn more</button>
                </div>
            </div>
