                <div class="card h-100" id="id">
                    <img src="../../static/img/images/Facial-Versus-Clean-up_1024x1024.png" id="height" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Facial cleansing</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">A procedure aimed at cleansing the skin, eliminating acne and comedones.
                        </p>
                        <div class="modal fade" id="staticBackdrop1" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false"
                            tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel1" aria-hidden="true">
                            <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-scrollable">
                                <div class="modal-content">
                                    <div class="modal-header">
                                        <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="staticBackdropLabel">Facial care</h1>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"
                                            aria-label="Close"></button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="modal-body">
                                        <p>
                                            Cleansing Techniques:
                                            Manual Cleansing: This involves using cleansers, exfoliants, and facial
                                            brushes or sponges to manually remove impurities from the skin's surface.
                                            Chemical Exfoliation: This method uses acids like alpha hydroxy acids (AHAs)
                                            or beta hydroxy acids (BHAs) to dissolve dead skin cells and unclog pores.
                                            <br>
                                            <hr>
                                            Professional vs. Home Facial Cleansing:
                                            Professional Facials: Conducted by licensed estheticians, professional
                                            facials often involve advanced techniques and specialized products tailored
                                            to individual skin needs.
                                            At-Home Care: Daily cleansing routines at home involve using suitable
                                            cleansers, exfoliants, and masks based on skin type and concerns.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button type="button" id="btn" class="btn btn-success" data-bs-toggle="modal"
                        data-bs-target="#staticBackdrop1">Learn more</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="../../static/img/images/botox-injection-botox-vs-fillers.jpg" id="height" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title"> Botox and fillers</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Using injections to reduce wrinkles and improve facial contours.</p>
                        <div class="modal fade" id="staticBackdrop2" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false"
                            tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel2" aria-hidden="true">
                            <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-scrollable">
                                <div class="modal-content">
                                    <div class="modal-header">
                                        <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="staticBackdropLabel">Manicure and pedicure</h1>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"
                                            aria-label="Close"></button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="modal-body">
                                        <p>
                                            Botox (Botulinum Toxin):
                                            How It Works: Botox is a neurotoxin that temporarily paralyzes or relaxes
                                            muscles, preventing them from contracting.
                                            This reduces the appearance of wrinkles caused by repetitive muscle
                                            movements, such as frown lines and crow's feet.
                                            <br>
                                            <hr>
                                            Dermal Fillers:
                                            Types of Fillers: Dermal fillers are substances injected beneath the skin to
                                            add volume, fill lines, and enhance facial
                                            contours. Common types include hyaluronic acid fillers, collagen fillers,
                                            and others.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button type="button" id="btn" class="btn btn-success" data-bs-toggle="modal"
                        data-bs-target="#staticBackdrop2">Learn more</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
