        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 g-4 px-5">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="../../static/img/images/microdermabrasion.jpg" id="height" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Microdermabrasion</h5>
                        <p class="card-text"> A mechanical exfoliation method that helps improve skin texture.</p>
                        <div class="modal fade" id="staticBackdrop3" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false"
                            tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel3" aria-hidden="true">
                            <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-scrollable">
                                <div class="modal-content">
                                    <div class="modal-header">
                                        <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="staticBackdropLabel">Hydrotherapy</h1>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"
                                            aria-label="Close"></button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="modal-body">
                                        <p>
                                            Procedure Overview:
                                            Mechanical Exfoliation: Microdermabrasion involves the use of a machine that
                                            emits fine crystals or a diamond-tipped wand to gently abrade the outer
                                            layer of the skin.
                                            Vacuum Suction: Simultaneously, a vacuum suction device removes the
                                            exfoliated skin cells, stimulating blood flow and promoting collagen
                                            production.
                                            <br>
                                            <hr>
                                            Purpose and Benefits:
                                            Exfoliation: Microdermabrasion exfoliates the outermost layer of dead skin
                                            cells, promoting cell turnover and revealing fresher, healthier skin.
                                            Improving Skin Texture: It helps address concerns such as rough skin
                                            texture, uneven pigmentation, and mild acne scars.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button type="button" id="btn" class="btn btn-success" data-bs-toggle="modal"
                        data-bs-target="#staticBackdrop3">Learn more</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="../../static/img/images/Hair-Mesotherapy.png" id="height" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Mesotherapy</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Introduction of special cocktails into the skin for hydration, nutrition
                            and rejuvenation.</p>
                        <div class="modal fade" id="staticBackdrop4" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false"
                            tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel4" aria-hidden="true">
                            <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-scrollable">
                                <div class="modal-content">
                                    <div class="modal-header">
                                        <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="staticBackdropLabel">Aromatherapy</h1>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"
                                            aria-label="Close"></button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="modal-body">
                                        <p>
                                            Purpose of Mesotherapy:
                                            Hydration: Mesotherapy helps improve skin hydration, making it useful for
                                            individuals with dry or dehydrated skin.
                                            Nutrition: The infusion of vitamins and minerals provides essential
                                            nutrients directly to the skin, promoting overall skin health.
                                            Rejuvenation: Mesotherapy is often used for facial rejuvenation, reducing
                                            the appearance of fine lines and promoting a more youthful complexion.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button type="button" id="btn" class="btn btn-success" data-bs-toggle="modal"
                        data-bs-target="#staticBackdrop4">Learn more</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="../../static/img/images/b5737206-e95.jpg" id="height" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Peels</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Chemical peels are designed to remove the top layers of skin to improve its
                            appearance and texture.</p>
                        <div class="modal fade" id="staticBackdrop5" data-bs-backdrop="static" data-bs-keyboard="false"
                            tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="staticBackdropLabel5" aria-hidden="true">
                            <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-scrollable">
                                <div class="modal-content">
                                    <div class="modal-header">
                                        <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="staticBackdropLabel">Wraps</h1>
                                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"
                                            aria-label="Close"></button>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="modal-body">
                                        <p>
                                            Types of Chemical Peels:
                                            Superficial Peels: These peels use mild acids, such as alpha hydroxy acids
                                            (AHAs) or beta hydroxy acids (BHAs), to exfoliate the outer layer of the
                                            skin. They are suitable for addressing minor skin concerns and require
                                            little to no downtime.
                                            Medium Peels: Medium-depth peels typically use stronger acids, such as
                                            trichloroacetic acid (TCA), to penetrate deeper into the skin. They are
                                            effective in treating more pronounced issues like fine lines, pigmentation,
                                            and acne scars.
                                            Deep Peels: Deep peels, often using phenol, penetrate the deepest layers of
                                            the skin. They are reserved for more severe skin concerns and are usually
                                            performed under sedation or general anesthesia.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button type="button" id="btn" class="btn btn-success" data-bs-toggle="modal"
                        data-bs-target="#staticBackdrop5">Learn more</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
